# Self-Interview App — Environment Variables
#
# The main .env.example is at the project root (../../.env.example).
# This app reads from the project root .env automatically.
#
# Quick start — add ONE of these to your root .env:
#
#   GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_...                    # Free, fast (recommended)
#   OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...                   # Paid, higher quality
#   NVIDIA_INFERENCE_KEY=nvapi-...          # NVIDIA Inference API
#
# Or use DEFAULT_PROVIDER + DEFAULT_MODEL for explicit control:
#
#   DEFAULT_PROVIDER=nvidia
#   DEFAULT_MODEL=aws/anthropic/bedrock-claude-opus-4-6
#
# See root .env.example for all options (storage, embeddings, custom endpoints).
